cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a model-based reinforcement learning approach that uses meta-policy optimization to quickly adapt to any model in an ensemble. This approach is designed to be more robust to model imperfections and requires less experience to match the asymptotic performance of model-free methods. Given these characteristics, the paper is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
